HEADWORD: Sphery
<hw>Spher"y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Round;
spherical; starlike.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Hermia's
<xex>sphery</xex> eyne.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
